reviews.review_text: World Music Theater 1990 All 3 of these shows were CRAZY good and bad! The music was great. However, the theater's lawn was guarded by a pretty small fence. Every night, 1000's of people jumped the fence as the shows started. Even police with dogs didn't stop people. Needless to say, the Dead never played there again. (Gate crashers suck)Sadly, these were Brent's last shows :'-( but he left on a high note.
